    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Faraway Lands: Rise of Yokai/遥远国度：妖怪崛起》是一款独特的横向卷轴基建生存游戏，背景设定在神秘的封建日本时代。作为新任领主，将你的定居点发展成要塞，在夜幕下抵御妖怪的猛攻。招募特质各异的移民，探索未知领域，结成新的联盟，并塑造光与暗撕裂之王国的命运。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/608864a7836ff8d5bac7a8bae98b10ca.webp?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=62 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/87756a44e604f915debdcd144db8fbad.poster.avif?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/87756a44e604f915debdcd144db8fbad.webm?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/87756a44e604f915debdcd144db8fbad.mp4?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙利用独特的山地地形，创建赏心悦目且高效运行的城镇，为基地建设游戏的爱好者提供了新颖的转折。你建造和升级的每一个结构都带来了新的可能性和挑战。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/685f7f527dbb7bd96826050319ebaacd.webp?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/02c8ee3fc25975c70d267ced67a12900.poster.avif?t=1771017994\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/02c8ee3fc25975c70d267ced67a12900.webm?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/02c8ee3fc25975c70d267ced67a12900.mp4?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过宝塔中学者驱动的动态研究系统，推进你的定居点发展。 通过分层进阶解锁强大的升级，塑造你城镇的未来。 随机化的研究选项让每次游戏体验保持新鲜，而专注于特定领域则让你能够调整策略以适应和繁荣发展。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/5c0e21f6e8972dcdb384c4a4caeacba9.webp?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=62 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/f1ae99a4d4b64f3511f0d82e14a1b021.poster.avif?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/f1ae99a4d4b64f3511f0d82e14a1b021.webm?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/f1ae99a4d4b64f3511f0d82e14a1b021.mp4?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的每一个居民都独一无二，他们特质各异，能力和效率不同。巧妙地将他们分配到各种工作上，如资源采集或制造，以此最大化城镇的生产力。平衡是关键——确保你的居民丰衣足食、身心健康和幸福安康，以此维持效率和人口增长。见证你的城镇从简单的定居点转变为繁荣的社区。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/7e63ea30dc47f087bd297bef66c83526.webp?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=62 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/a49ebd3b987e28fab29a691480bfe947.poster.avif?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/a49ebd3b987e28fab29a691480bfe947.webm?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/a49ebd3b987e28fab29a691480bfe947.mp4?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜幕降临时，你的战略技巧将受到可怕妖怪的考验。训练各种不同的士兵，从挥舞致命刀剑的强大武士到操控魂灵的神秘阴阳师，引领他们保卫你的城镇。雇佣熟练的雇佣兵，利用他们的独特才能守卫你的城镇。战略性地部署士兵来守卫你的城镇边界。每一个夜晚都是对你防御策略和适应力的考验。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/64a054f7a849ccb173f504fa60b73874.webp?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=62 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/8b4dcb33ba301c666fffec40e495f2f2.poster.avif?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/8b4dcb33ba301c666fffec40e495f2f2.webm?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/8b4dcb33ba301c666fffec40e495f2f2.mp4?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索边境之外，发现广阔无垠的世界。勘探未知领域，遭遇海盗，揭开神秘岛屿的面纱。与新国家建立贸易路线，用稀有资源和异国奖励丰富你的基地。深入探索地表之下，挖掘宝贵矿石、勘探神秘洞穴，以及埋藏在城镇之下的秘密。你所发现的可能正是抗衡妖怪的利器。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/3539208ce0b8cf26c7ecce21b910050c.webp?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=62 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/3842dcde5fd11ad2d39475fba4400d55.poster.avif?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/3842dcde5fd11ad2d39475fba4400d55.webm?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/3842dcde5fd11ad2d39475fba4400d55.mp4?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验充满动态天气和变化季节构成的鲜活世界，这些变化会带来独特的挑战和美景。严阵以待，应对考验你管理技能的自然灾害。你将如何适应自然的变化？ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/1f7727758e85d1f7f7f40b8752840a5c.webp?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=62 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/22600a59834a0c52b086eefea6a55456.poster.avif?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/22600a59834a0c52b086eefea6a55456.webm?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/22600a59834a0c52b086eefea6a55456.mp4?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种种独特的遗物和领主丰富你的游戏体验。每位领主都为城镇带来不同的风格，遗物则提供新的游戏动力。尝试不同的组合，每次游玩都能获得全新体验。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/8bdf7f4f21a4495a175b0dd6229f5787.webp?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=62 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/29cb1b0e33a2227aa88477da25bd50d1.poster.avif?t=1771017994\" width=614 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/29cb1b0e33a2227aa88477da25bd50d1.webm?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303940/extras/29cb1b0e33a2227aa88477da25bd50d1.mp4?t=1771017994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅仅要创造功能性的城镇，更要在丰富的像素艺术风格中创造令人赏心悦目的城镇。利用各种装饰品为你的城镇增添美感和魅力。从盆栽到华丽的雕像，每次点缀都让你的城镇更加独具一格、引人入胜。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
